BY ROTIMI AGBANA It is generally believed that a lady’s beauty creates opportunities for her in unbelievable ways. This is also the belief of alluring Anambra State born model, Julian Adans, an intelligent, young and enticing woman who sees great prospects in flaunting her beautiful endowments. For the pretty model, her greatest asset is her irresistible beauty. She said, “My great looks have opened lots of doors for me which literally wouldn’t have opened if I wasn’t beautiful. She opined that even if she believes in creativity and intelligence, beauty comes first for her. In her words, “People get attracted first to your looks before finding out how creative, intelligent and productive you are.” Julian who spends a fortune making sure she stands out with her looks anywhere she goes advised ladies to take good care of themselves and be very keen about how they look because she believes good looks open doors for ladies more than any other thing. The post Being attractive opens doors for me — Julian Adans appeared first on Vanguard News. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from Vanguard News. Click here to read the full text on the original website.